Rooms at Le Minh 2 Guest House offer air conditioning, a minibar, and a seating area providing exceptional comfort and convenience. Close to some of Can Tho's most popular landmarks, such as Can Tho Museum (0.8 mi) and Pitu Khosa Rangsay (0.9 mi), Le Minh 2 Guest House is a great destination for tourists. When you’re feeling hungry, be sure to check out Bo Tung Xeo Nu Nhi Hong, Suon Cong Bbq & Hotpot, and Rooftop Bar, which are some pubs that are popular with locals and out-of-towners alike. Looking to explore? Then look no further than Hai Ba Trung Street (1.2 mi), which is a popular Can Tho attraction – and it is conveniently located within walking distance of the small hotel. Le Minh 2 Guest House is sure to make your visit to Can Tho one worth remembering.
